<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 40px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
            
            <!-- HEADER -->
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #111827; padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
                <!-- LOGO -->
                <img src="https://itan-bucket-storage.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/itan-logo.jpg" width="120" style="display:block; margin: 0 auto 12px auto;" />
                <!-- Tagline -->
                <p style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; margin: 0;">
                  Not just stories—epic experiences told in the rhythm of Africa
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- BODY -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 40px 30px; text-align: left;">
                <h2 style="color: #111827; margin: 0 0 20px 0; text-align: center;">Welcome to ITAN</h2>
                
                <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  <strong>Dear <%= @reader.first_name %>,</strong>
                </p>

                <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  We‘re thrilled to have you join <strong>ITAN</strong> — the home of African Literature. 
                  From timeless classics to modern voices, ITAN connects readers like you with stories 
                  that inspire, educate, and celebrate African culture.
                </p>

                <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Start exploring a wide range of books—from children’s stories and comics to contemporary fiction, 
                  fantasy, speculative fiction, romance, and more. Step into the vibrant world of African storytelling.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- FOOTER -->
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #f2f2f2; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">
                © <%= Time.current.year %> ITAN. All rights reserved.
                <br /><br />
                <span style="color: #555555; font-size: 13px;">
                  From all of us at ITAN <br />
                  For enquiries, reach us at <a href="mailto:support@itan.app" style="color: #b91c1c; text-decoration: none;">support@itan.app</a>
                </span>
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>

